Synthetic re-construction of upstream bug fix
779e7d5534b9ab5367e2924964af4b906454f969 ("Fix Read instance of Bit").

The buggy Read Bit instance returned Bit False for the input character
'1', breaking the `read . show` round-trip for Bit True.

Reverse-applying installs the bug; forward-applying restores the fix.

diff --git a/src/Data/Bit/Internal.hs b/src/Data/Bit/Internal.hs
--- a/src/Data/Bit/Internal.hs
+++ b/src/Data/Bit/Internal.hs
@@ -118,7 +118,7 @@ instance Read Bit where
 instance Read Bit where
   readsPrec p (' ' : rest) = readsPrec p rest
   readsPrec _ ('0' : rest) = [(Bit False, rest)]
-  readsPrec _ ('1' : rest) = [(Bit False, rest)]
+  readsPrec _ ('1' : rest) = [(Bit True, rest)]
   readsPrec _ _            = []

 instance U.Unbox Bit
